how do you delete node modules? @John St
i built nginx on build machine this morning from master fine.  quick call @Heymian ?
The directory to delete is webserver/shared/src/js/webpacked/node_modules, then you'd run yarn install in webpacked
oh let me try that first! thank you both!
yup @Jessica - i guess deleting the dir is sufficient, the build-docker takes care of yarn install as well?

@Heymian I had to run
```rm yarn.lock && yarn```
in
```webserver/shared/src/js/webpacked```
to resolve the issue
sweet that worked! thanks all! :pray: appreciate the help at this late hour!
